Name: samcat
Author: David Weese <david.weese@fu-berlin.de>
Maintainer: David Weese <david.weese@fu-berlin.de>
License: GPL v3
Copyright: 2008-2014, FU Berlin
Status: under development
Description: Concatenate SAM or BAM files.
 This tool reads a set of input files in SAM or BAM format and outputs the
 concatenation of them. If the output file name is ommitted the result is
 written to standard output in SAM format.
